Package: lithicscarpattern
Title: Lithic Flaking Scar Orientation Alignment and Spherical Harmonic Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Your", "Name", , "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A complete toolkit for the geometric alignment, spherical
    harmonic decomposition, and statistical analysis of three-dimensional
    lithic flaking scar orientation data. Provides two alignment pipelines
    (SVD and Lin 2024), classical orientation statistics (SPI, E, I), and
    spherical harmonic analysis via a Python backend (von Mises-Fisher
    kernel density estimation followed by Driscoll-Healy spherical harmonic
    expansion using pyshtools).
